################################################################################
# Terraform Backend Configuration (Optional)
#
# Uncomment and configure one of the backends below for remote state storage.
# This is recommended for production deployments and team collaboration.
#
# To use a backend:
# 1. Uncomment the desired backend block
# 2. Configure the backend parameters
# 3. Run: terraform init (Terraform will ask to migrate state)
# 4. Commit this file to version control
################################################################################

